Package fastily.jwiki.util

Classes with static methods that support the jwiki core framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FL
    Static Collections and Stream utilities.
    FSystem
    System properties and static error handling methods.
    GroupQueue<T>
    A simple read-only Queue that allows multiple items to be polled at once.
    GSONP
    Static utility methods for use with Gson.
    MultiMap<K,V>
    A HashMap which allows multiple values for each key.
    Triple<X,Y,Z>
    A simple implementation of a 3-set of immutable values.
    Tuple<K,V>
    Simple implementation of a Tuple.
    WikiGen
    A simple console based-credential manager.

Package fastily.jwiki.util Description

Classes with static methods that support the jwiki core framework. These are very general, and may be helpful in applications that build on jwiki.

jwiki is licensed under the terms of the GPLv3.
Author:
Fastily
